title: FC Babaque
text: F.C. Babaque is a <a href="Bissau-Guinean">Bissau-Guinean</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Farim">Farim</a>. They play in the 2 division in Guinean football, the <a href="Campeonato%20Nacional%20da%20Guine-Bissau">Campeonato Nacional da Guine-Bissau</a>.
